<doc id="501637" wikidata="Q341493" url="?curid=501637" title="Landsting">
<text>Landsting may refer to:

* Thing (assembly), the supreme assembly of a &quot;land&quot; in Scandinavia, during Viking and Medieval times
* Parliament of Greenland
* Landsting (Denmark), one of the two houses of the Danish parliament between 1849 and 1953
* Regions of Sweden, formerly known as Landsting.</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q387834" start="27" end="43" title="Thing (assembly)" label="Thing (assembly)"/>
